1
00:01:24,460 --> 00:01:29,979
[One and Only]

2
00:01:29,979 --> 00:01:32,979
[Episode 11]

3
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:33,680
Stay where you are!

4
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:37,000
Yang Shao, let go of Feng Qiao.

5
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,039
Don't come close, Shiyi.

6
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,160
I have but one request.

7
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,759
Give me Liu Changshan.

8
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:43,039
What do you want him for?

9
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:43,960
That's none of your business.

10
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:44,960
Just bring him here.

11
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:46,479
Go get him.

12
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,280
Yes.

13
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,600
Don't come close.

14
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,840
Yang Shao,

15
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:55,960
if I had known

16
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,320
you were so ungrateful,

17
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,560
I wouldn't have helped you.

18
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,640
Miss Cui,

19
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,199
I have my reason to save him.

20
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,120
Stay where you are!

21
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,160
Don't push him.

22
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,600
He won't hurt Shiyi.

23
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,760
General Yang.

24
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,400
You are finally here to save me.

25
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,840
Cut the crap and come with me.

26
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:27,040
Prepare a carriage for me

27
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,000
outside the city.

28
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:29,360
Prepare a carriage.

29
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:30,200
Yes.

30
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,400
Please excuse me, Miss Cui.

31
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,560
You don't know Kung Fu,

32
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:34,920
which makes you a better choice as a hostage.

33
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,320
Come.

34
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:53,740
[Yongcheng]

35
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,080
You drive the carriage!

36
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,160
Your Highness,

37
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,600
I won't hurt her.

38
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:02,920
You can follow me.

39
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,520
Once I make it to Nanxiao in one piece,

40
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,960
I will let her go.

41
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,080
Yang Shao,

42
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,640
if you so much as harm a hair on her head,

43
00:03:10,330 --> 00:03:11,420
whether you go beyond south of the river,

44
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,760
the Gobi Desert in the west,

45
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,320
or even to the underworld,

46
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:15,670
I will personally

47
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,680
take your life.

48
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,920
I have no other choice.

49
00:03:19,250 --> 00:03:20,880
Your Highness, I am sorry for doing this.

50
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,520
Get me a horse!

51
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,200
Yes, Your Highness.

52
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:37,560
Xiao Yan, do something.

53
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,160
Nanxiao is your homeland.

54
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,200
The transportation between the South and the North is smooth.

55
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,320
It won't be a problem for them to go there.

56
00:03:43,270 --> 00:03:44,400
However, since it is His Highness,

57
00:03:44,410 --> 00:03:45,770
it would definitely cause a stir

58
00:03:46,570 --> 00:03:48,040
if people found out he was in Nanxiao.

59
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,600
Isn't that obvious?

60
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,560
Scouting Camp,

61
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:54,720
get on your horses.

62
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,960
We'll follow them in secret to protect His Highness and Shiyi.

63
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:57,840
Yes!

64
00:04:35,780 --> 00:04:36,540
I have been holding the sword

65
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:37,980
all this way.

66
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:40,780
My arm is about to come off.

67
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,880
You are being followed by Zhousheng Chen.

68
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,880
You dare to lower that sword

69
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,200
but have not fear of being decapitated?

70
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,200
General Yang,

71
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:52,040
the best thing I ever did in my life

72
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,960
was putting in a good word for you.

73
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,840
There's not much to eat around here,

74
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:57,720
so have some of this.

75
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:00,880
Master hasn't eaten anything

76
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,200
for a day.

77
00:05:12,860 --> 00:05:13,750
He cares a lot about you.

78
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:18,030
Otherwise, why would a noble prince

79
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:19,030
be willing to risk his life coming here alone

80
00:05:19,150 --> 00:05:20,190
and follow you to Nanxiao?

81
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,240
He is my master.

82
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,400
Whatever it is,

83
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,520
he cares about you.

84
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:33,560
My oh my.

85
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,360
It turns out

86
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:38,320
your affair

87
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:39,120
is no less serious than

88
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,960
my treason.

89
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:43,040
Aren't you marrying the Prince of Guangling?

90
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,680
The engagement was canceled.

91
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,320
He is just my master.

92
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:56,920
When we make it to Nanxiao tomorrow,

93
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,520
remember you mustn't say anything about who you are.

94
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:00,600
If someone found out and came after you,

95
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:01,840
I can't guarantee your safety.

96
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,360
Have some of this.

97
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,080
Give it to my master.

98
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,760
This is the only chicken I got.

99
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,640
Even I feel reluctant to eat it.

100
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,240
He hasn't eaten anything

101
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,400
for a day and a night.

102
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,000
There's two of you

103
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,159
so you two can take turns to hunt for food.

104
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,360
But he can only starve.

105
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,840
If you don't give him food,

106
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:31,159
I am not going to eat either.

107
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,040
I'll have it.

108
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,600
The master-disciple relationship you have sure is touching.

109
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,600
Here's some food your disciple got for you!

110
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:06,120
I will charter the two boats.

111
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:08,760
This one,

112
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:12,800
is for him.

113
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,000
My mother said

114
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,800
you had to come back to Jingling with me this time

115
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:23,160
and you had to explain to them

116
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,000
in person,

117
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:24,960
about why you married my sister without their consent.

118
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,240
If you can't give an explanation,

119
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,640
she will not be coming back with you.

120
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,200
Get on the boat.

121
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,800
The bastard's full of tricks.

122
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:55,760
General,

123
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:56,920
what do we do now?

124
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,360
Get our men to the bank of the river

125
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,840
and wait for furthur orders.

126
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,160
If their identity is exposed,

127
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,960
we need to be ready to cross the river.

128
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,840
Set sail, follow him.

129
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,680
Go to Shouyang immediately

130
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,800
and tell General Cui

131
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,400
to get ready to send out troops.

132
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,480
Yes.

133
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,640
You northerners

134
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,000
love to elope, huh?

135
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,400
Not really.

136
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,120
I won't blame your brother-in-law

137
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,120
for being so mad.

138
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,800
You have to go back with him,

139
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:48,320
prepare a bride-price, perform a formal wedding ceremony,

140
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,080
and bow before your parents to express your gratitude for their upbringing.

141
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,240
After that,

142
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,880
you bring your bride home.

143
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:57,520
All right.

144
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,080
However,

145
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,200
the lady over there is constantly looking back.

146
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,680
I guess it won't be hard for you

147
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,080
this time.

148
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,240
You know how parents are.

149
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,440
As long as their daughter shows affection,

150
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:07,800
they won't give you a hard time.

151
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:12,960
You can see

152
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,400
that she's into me?

153
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,760
The moment you stepped on the boat,

154
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:18,520
her gaze

155
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:19,760
were fixed on you.

156
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:21,160
Who do you think is in her heart

157
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,440
other than you?

158
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:42,480
This is your first time to Nanxiao?

159
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:56,760
You saved me twice, I owe you.

160
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,080
This is a military stronghold of the South.

161
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,160
Be careful of what you say.

162
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,040
Let's go.

163
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:25,600
Give me the Tiger Tally.

164
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:26,800
Yang Shao,

165
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,360
did you bring me to Nanxiao

166
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:33,080
just for the tally?

167
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:35,600
The favor of your recommendation

168
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,560
is now returned.

169
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,440
I will give you a hint to save yourself.

170
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,600
Bring the news of the second Prince, Xiaoyan

171
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,360
to the Emperor of Nanxiao.

172
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,560
He loves his son very much,

173
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,720
thus he will for sure accommodate you.

174
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,040
Now hand out the Tiger Tally.

175
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:58,120
The rest of your stragglers

176
00:10:58,520 --> 00:10:59,480
are now mine.

177
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,800
What are you doing?

178
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:05,840
I hate a ruthless traitor like you

179
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:07,520
the most.

180
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:08,840
The next time I see you,

181
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,400
I will kill you myself.

182
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:25,520
It's all my fault that I got you involved.

183
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:28,320
It's nothing like that.

184
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,440
If it weren't for this occasion,

185
00:11:30,990 --> 00:11:31,510
I am afraid

186
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:33,270
you will never get the chance to come here.

187
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,800
You said it as if you set this up

188
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:36,960
on purpose.

189
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,600
But seriously,

190
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,960
I had given some thoughts that

191
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,960
one day when the Central Plains are united,

192
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,240
I'll take you here.

193
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:50,800
It's true.

194
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,200
Move aside!

195
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:57,280
Out of the way!

196
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:12,200
Why did you let out a sigh, Master?

197
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,720
It just occurred to me

198
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,000
that you had never

199
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,240
fought alongside me.

200
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:19,640
What a pity.

201
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,400
We can do that in the future.

202
00:12:26,860 --> 00:12:29,000
Yeah, we can.

203
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:38,480
Guards, hurry!

204
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,760
I need to see your prefectural governor.

205
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:40,120
Now!

206
00:12:40,400 --> 00:12:41,320
Who are you?

207
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:42,600
I am a member of the royal family of Beichen.

208
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,400
Liu Changshan.

209
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,160
Bring me to your prefectural governor, now.

210
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:45,880
General.

211
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,200
What's the fuss about?

212
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,960
The junior Prince of Nanchen is in the city.

213
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,760
Bring me to see your prefectural governor, now!

214
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,160
Who did you say it was?

215
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,600
The junior Prince of Nanchen.

216
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,880
Zhousheng Chen!

217
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:56,760
Close the city gate.

218
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,960
There is a carriage pulled by goats.

219
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,120
People in Jiangling

220
00:13:16,410 --> 00:13:17,480
are pretty unconstrained.

221
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,200
Not only do they use goats to pull carts.

222
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:21,280
There was even a General Shen in the Former Song Dynasty,

223
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,520
who would ride a bizarre carriage

224
00:13:22,640 --> 00:13:24,000
every time he met the emperor.

225
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:26,680
It was called the pig-nose valance-less car.

226
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:28,480
All the officials didn't think it was strange.

227
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,000
On the contrary, they loved it.

228
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,680
Pig-nose valance-less car?

229
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,720
Get out of the way, get out of the way!

230
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:40,480
Get out of the way, get out of the way!

231
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,560
Get out of the way, get out of the way!

232
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:42,640
Get out of the way!

233
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,640
What do you think happened?

234
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,360
Why are there so many troops?

235
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:47,560
I'll tell you what,

236
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:49,040
the junior Prince of Nanchen is right here in the city.

237
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:50,360
No one knows what happened.

238
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:51,240
Isn't...

239
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,800
Isn't there a peace treaty between the South and the North?

240
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:54,080
Exactly! Why did the prince come here

241
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,640
when everything is okay?

242
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,120
The city gates are now closed

243
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:59,000
and no one is allowed to go in or out.

244
00:13:59,680 --> 00:14:00,360
Let' get out of here.

245
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,720
Let's go home, go home now.

246
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,520
Let's go.

247
00:14:03,560 --> 00:14:05,680
It looks like we are going to stay here a few more days.

248
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:08,200
Are we not figuring out a way to send information out of the city?

249
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:09,760
There is no hurry.

250
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,640
So where are we going now?

251
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:15,460
Let's go to someone I know here.

252
00:14:16,450 --> 00:14:18,280
You know someone in the South?

253
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:21,970
An old friend of mine who happens to be around here.

254
00:14:35,750 --> 00:14:36,770
It's so beautiful here.

255
00:14:37,430 --> 00:14:38,960
Adjacent to the river and the mountain.

256
00:14:41,180 --> 00:14:42,830
It would be great if we could unite the Central Plains sooner.

257
00:14:43,030 --> 00:14:44,190
So that people from the south could see

258
00:14:44,350 --> 00:14:45,470
our lofty ancient cities and vast deserts

259
00:14:45,950 --> 00:14:47,670
and we could enjoy the mountains and rivers here.

260
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:48,230
How nice that would be.

261
00:14:50,590 --> 00:14:51,910
There's still an hour's walk,

262
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:53,070
can you take it?

263
00:14:54,190 --> 00:14:55,190
When Master was away,

264
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:56,590
I used to go around

265
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:57,310
all the temples in the Western State

266
00:14:57,470 --> 00:14:59,270
to lit up incense and pray for the Royal Army.

267
00:14:59,430 --> 00:15:00,750
That's why I got strong legs.

268
00:15:01,350 --> 00:15:03,550
You can't call me "Master" here.

269
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:04,560
It will reveal our identity.

270
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:06,570
Yes, Master.

271
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:11,960
I understood.

272
00:15:18,820 --> 00:15:20,140
Are you going up the mountain?

273
00:15:20,620 --> 00:15:21,060
Yes.

274
00:15:21,300 --> 00:15:22,500
Then you need to hurry.

275
00:15:22,660 --> 00:15:23,420
The teacher of this academy

276
00:15:23,580 --> 00:15:24,420
is grumpy

277
00:15:24,620 --> 00:15:25,300
and won't receive visitors

278
00:15:25,300 --> 00:15:26,540
after sunset.

279
00:15:27,260 --> 00:15:29,020
It doesn't matter if you have to spend the night in the mountains,

280
00:15:29,260 --> 00:15:30,140
it's just that

281
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:31,940
your wife would have a hard time.

282
00:15:52,060 --> 00:15:52,740
What?

283
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:57,580
This is a land full of great people and natural wonders.

