568
00:30:47,050 --> 00:30:48,950
and help them escape to the South.

569
00:30:50,750 --> 00:30:52,730
There was also a branch of the Cui family that once traveled to the South.

570
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:55,560
Some of the aristocratic families went to South to seek asylum,

571
00:30:55,780 --> 00:30:57,580
while some went to the North to earn a living.

572
00:30:58,250 --> 00:30:59,740
They are like wild geese migrating between the North and the South

573
00:30:59,910 --> 00:31:00,890
in order to survive.

574
00:31:02,190 --> 00:31:02,860
Yeah.

575
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:04,860
Like the people we met

576
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:05,740
who fled their hometown.

577
00:31:06,520 --> 00:31:07,420
They were all doing this

578
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:08,260
just to survive.

579
00:31:26,060 --> 00:31:27,060
I haven't lived a laid-back life like this

580
00:31:27,180 --> 00:31:28,300
for a long time.

581
00:31:30,980 --> 00:31:31,900
My senior brothers and senior sisters

582
00:31:32,020 --> 00:31:33,180
must be terribly worried,

583
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:34,460
yet you say we're having a laid-back time.

584
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:36,220
In the past,

585
00:31:36,340 --> 00:31:37,820
I have always been the one who worried about them.

586
00:31:37,940 --> 00:31:39,410
Now it's their turn

587
00:31:39,520 --> 00:31:40,620
to worry about me.

588
00:31:41,580 --> 00:31:42,660
You are the master

589
00:31:42,780 --> 00:31:43,980
but you still care about that?

590
00:31:45,060 --> 00:31:45,940
Don't you remember?

591
00:31:46,130 --> 00:31:46,900
Xiaoyu and Tianxing

592
00:31:46,970 --> 00:31:48,080
are about my age.

593
00:31:48,730 --> 00:31:49,820
While other disciples

594
00:31:49,940 --> 00:31:50,990
are only a few years younger than me.

595
00:31:52,940 --> 00:31:54,300
That's what the monk said as well.

596
00:31:56,980 --> 00:31:58,060
Only he

597
00:31:58,180 --> 00:31:59,460
knows how hard it is for me.

598
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:01,380
I know as well.

599
00:32:07,140 --> 00:32:08,860
You did it on purpose.

600
00:32:09,820 --> 00:32:10,780
Did what on purpose?

601
00:32:11,020 --> 00:32:13,020
To air your grievances and get my empathy.

602
00:32:13,340 --> 00:32:14,300
Why would I

603
00:32:14,420 --> 00:32:15,620
lie to you yo get your empathy?

604
00:32:17,900 --> 00:32:18,900
I give up.

605
00:32:20,580 --> 00:32:22,140
All right, time to sleep.

606
00:32:31,300 --> 00:32:32,580
Why are you not sleeping on the bed

607
00:32:32,830 --> 00:32:33,860
but on the floor?

608
00:32:35,060 --> 00:32:36,500
I have slept on the floor before.

609
00:32:37,060 --> 00:32:39,420
The day you took me to see the retainers,

610
00:32:39,740 --> 00:32:41,540
I slept in you study.

611
00:32:41,780 --> 00:32:43,220
That was on the floor as well.

612
00:32:45,220 --> 00:32:46,220
That time,

613
00:32:46,340 --> 00:32:48,020
you covered me with a fox fur

614
00:32:48,100 --> 00:32:49,340
and carried me back in your arms.

615
00:32:50,780 --> 00:32:51,940
That fox fur

616
00:32:52,100 --> 00:32:53,620
is still kept in my room.

617
00:32:54,060 --> 00:32:55,500
If you like it,

618
00:32:55,740 --> 00:32:57,220
I can make a new one for you.

619
00:33:01,990 --> 00:33:03,160
That's the only one I like.

620
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:52,060
Your Highness,

621
00:33:52,860 --> 00:33:54,260
you have been staring at it all night.

622
00:33:54,740 --> 00:33:55,700
It's time for you to take your medicine.

623
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:59,620
Why don't you love me?

624
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:03,020
You would rather be a disciple

625
00:34:03,139 --> 00:34:03,780
of Zhousheng Chen

626
00:34:03,940 --> 00:34:04,620
than marry me

627
00:34:04,739 --> 00:34:06,139
and become a prestigious princess.

628
00:34:10,699 --> 00:34:12,020
If you want,

629
00:34:12,940 --> 00:34:14,739
I can give up everything for you.

630
00:34:14,940 --> 00:34:15,860
I can bring you out of the Central State,

631
00:34:15,980 --> 00:34:17,219
this troubled land.

632
00:34:23,699 --> 00:34:24,179
Yes.

633
00:34:25,179 --> 00:34:26,780
I may not understand this kind of thing,

634
00:34:27,659 --> 00:34:28,260
but Your Highness can't

635
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:30,020
overlook your own health.

636
00:34:31,020 --> 00:34:32,659
Please take your medicine first.

637
00:34:37,020 --> 00:34:38,340
Put it here

638
00:34:38,460 --> 00:34:39,460
and leave.

639
00:34:43,540 --> 00:34:44,100
Yes, Your Highness.

640
00:35:09,620 --> 00:35:10,940
They are all students from impoverished families.

641
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,720
They heard that someone from the Cui family came to the academy,

642
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:14,540
and vied to get the opportunity

643
00:35:14,660 --> 00:35:15,660
to talk about poetry and Taoism with you.

644
00:35:23,330 --> 00:35:24,620
You've read a lot of books since you were a kid.

645
00:35:25,020 --> 00:35:26,060
Just share your opinion with them

646
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:27,260
as a pastime.

647
00:35:28,380 --> 00:35:30,140
Though I have read plenty, I may not understand everything.

648
00:35:31,580 --> 00:35:32,540
Take me and Zhousheng Chen for example,

649
00:35:32,700 --> 00:35:33,620
people at our age

650
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:35,540
won't say that we understand everything we read.

651
00:35:36,220 --> 00:35:37,340
In terms of the amount of book collections in the North,

652
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:38,740
the Cui family comes first.

653
00:35:39,460 --> 00:35:40,300
Most of what you have read,

654
00:35:40,420 --> 00:35:41,420
I have never had the privilage

655
00:35:41,540 --> 00:35:42,180
to read them.

656
00:35:42,460 --> 00:35:43,900
It would be of great help

657
00:35:44,220 --> 00:35:45,620
if you can share it with all of them.

658
00:35:47,100 --> 00:35:48,940
After hearing what you said, I'm glad to do it.

659
00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:55,060
I'm not skilled or very knowledgeable,

660
00:35:55,140 --> 00:35:55,660
I merely took advantage of

661
00:35:55,780 --> 00:35:57,340
the book collections at home.

662
00:35:57,460 --> 00:35:59,420
Please don't take my words too seriously

663
00:35:59,540 --> 00:36:00,420
and treat this as a casual exchange.

664
00:36:01,180 --> 00:36:02,500
We'd be more than happy

665
00:36:02,660 --> 00:36:04,500
to have you share your thoughts.

666
00:36:04,620 --> 00:36:05,500
This way please.

667
00:36:10,540 --> 00:36:12,780
This is brilliant.

668
00:36:20,020 --> 00:36:20,900
How do you feel for the first time

669
00:36:21,020 --> 00:36:22,620
that you are not surrounded

670
00:36:22,980 --> 00:36:23,820
by everyone?

671
00:36:25,160 --> 00:36:25,760
Great.

672
00:36:28,580 --> 00:36:29,210
I'm sure

673
00:36:29,620 --> 00:36:30,940
you'll be like me in the future,

674
00:36:31,100 --> 00:36:31,780
a person that fears his wife.

675
00:36:34,940 --> 00:36:36,060
What?

676
00:36:40,260 --> 00:36:40,740
Brilliant!

677
00:36:41,180 --> 00:36:42,140
Impressive, impressive!

678
00:36:52,860 --> 00:36:53,820
You are watching them shoot arrows?

679
00:37:00,180 --> 00:37:01,020
Wanna have a try?

680
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:06,060
Go and try it.

681
00:37:07,580 --> 00:37:08,660
Is it allowed in the academy?

682
00:37:08,740 --> 00:37:09,580
For an outsider to do this?

683
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:10,680
I am in charge here

684
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:11,580
while he commands the army.

685
00:37:11,820 --> 00:37:12,900
Who dares to say no?

686
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:20,940
She seems to like lively places.

687
00:37:22,260 --> 00:37:23,940
It's rare for her to be somewhere there are many people.

688
00:37:24,560 --> 00:37:25,550
I was often away from my mansion.

689
00:37:26,380 --> 00:37:27,180
For the past few years,

690
00:37:27,340 --> 00:37:28,700
she was only accompanied by one of her servants

691
00:37:28,910 --> 00:37:30,080
and the home library.

692
00:37:32,140 --> 00:37:33,140
Having heard that,

693
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,340
she is indeed a poor girl.

694
00:37:48,260 --> 00:37:50,100
Impressive, very impressive.

695
00:37:50,180 --> 00:37:51,340
Look at that, that's really something.

696
00:37:51,340 --> 00:37:52,100
Did you teach her?

697
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:55,300
I have never taught her archery.

698
00:37:55,940 --> 00:37:56,620
Mas...

699
00:38:00,020 --> 00:38:01,100
Did you see that?

700
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:06,800
Who taught you that?

701
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:10,140
The mansion's shooting range is always empty

702
00:38:10,260 --> 00:38:11,140
and I found myself idle most of the time.

703
00:38:11,300 --> 00:38:12,020
So I learnt it secretly.

704
00:38:14,460 --> 00:38:15,740
You're fairly accurate.

705
00:38:15,900 --> 00:38:17,340
But your posture needs fixing.

706
00:38:24,830 --> 00:38:25,150
Here.

707
00:38:41,870 --> 00:38:42,410
Ready.

708
00:38:42,410 --> 00:38:46,450
♫Like a gust of wind gently brushing♫

709
00:38:48,830 --> 00:38:53,000
♫Like a cloud waiting for the rain to fall♫

710
00:38:55,460 --> 00:38:57,830
♫There is a corner in my heart♫

711
00:38:58,600 --> 00:39:01,030
♫Where my expectation is glowing♫

712
00:39:01,460 --> 00:39:06,630
♫It's the shooting star lighting up the night sky for you♫

713
00:39:10,860 --> 00:39:11,860
The bows in our academy are

714
00:39:12,140 --> 00:39:13,180
all given by the hunters.

715
00:39:13,580 --> 00:39:14,180
They are not

716
00:39:14,300 --> 00:39:15,420
as light as the ones from your mansion.

717
00:39:16,140 --> 00:39:17,300
I should've warned you

718
00:39:17,460 --> 00:39:18,620
so that you wouldn't injure your shoulders.

719
00:39:21,940 --> 00:39:23,660
She needs help with the injury behind her shoulder.

720
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:33,620
I can apply it myself.

721
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:36,620
This medicine

722
00:39:36,780 --> 00:39:38,180
requires some rubbing with your palms

723
00:39:38,300 --> 00:39:39,220
in order to take effect.

724
00:39:42,180 --> 00:39:43,060
It's a pity

725
00:39:43,460 --> 00:39:45,020
that my academy is full of male students.

726
00:39:45,300 --> 00:39:46,580
So no one can help you.

727
00:39:47,180 --> 00:39:48,460
Do you mind

728
00:39:48,620 --> 00:39:50,380
asking your wife to help me?

729
00:39:53,380 --> 00:39:54,460
She won't see visitors.

730
00:39:56,580 --> 00:39:57,300
Help yourselves.

731
00:39:57,420 --> 00:39:58,420
I will leave you two be.

732
00:40:13,580 --> 00:40:14,630
Apply the medicine on your own first

733
00:40:16,370 --> 00:40:18,000
and call me after you've covered your shoulder with a cloth.

734
00:40:51,100 --> 00:40:52,260
I am ready.

735
00:41:41,660 --> 00:41:43,060
Did I

736
00:41:43,460 --> 00:41:45,260
say something wrong just now?

737
00:41:48,860 --> 00:41:50,940
You mean about Mrs. Huan?

738
00:41:55,180 --> 00:41:55,900
I'll find a time

739
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:58,340
and take you to see her later.
